Please create a professional technical resume using the following strict Markdown structure.

Use exactly `## Heading` (not bold text and no other styles and no trailing space after Heading) for each section.
Bullet points must start with `- ` and be on separate lines.
Do not use any additional formatting styles (no bold, italics, or extra symbols).

Here is the required format:

## Profile Summary

{user_input_profile_summary}

## Competencies

{user_input_competencies}

## Education

{user_input_education}

## Certification

{user_input_certification}

## Work Experience

{user_input_experience}

Only return the resume in Markdown format with no trailing space after Summary, Competencies, Education, Certification and Work Experience headings. Refine sections as per professional resume.
